input.sql:
select 
    opportunity_numbers
    ,trx_date_fiscal_quarter_shortname
    ,trx_date_fiscal_year_number
    ,trx_date_fiscal_year_name
    ,trx_crm_forecast_category
    ,ordered_quantity_min
    ,product_split_offering_group
    ,trx_partner_mdm_party_id
    ,snapshot_date
    ,acv_amount_usd_cy_pr
    ,source_system
    ,usage_type
    ,account_type
    ,source_id
    ,account_id
    ,member_id
    ,journal_type_id
    ,journal_subtype_id
    ,transaction_journal_id
    ,'Pending' AS STATUS
    ,'#{_dp('{"pill_type":"output","provider":"workato_variable","line":"5e2fb07a","path":["uat_loyalty_record_id"]}')}' AS RECORD_TYPE_ID
    ,'#{_dp('{"pill_type":"job_context","path":["user_name"]}')}' AS USERNAME
 from PARTNERPROGRAMS_DB.MARTS.LOYALTY_STAGE_TJ
 where transaction_journal_id is null
